《'''瘋狂前女友'''》（{{lang-en|''Crazy Ex-Girlfriend''}}）是一部於2015年10月12日在[[CW電視網|The CW]]開播的美國[[歌舞片|歌舞]][[喜劇|喜劇]]。<ref name="announcement">{{cite web |last=Bibel |first=Sara |title=The CW Announces Fall 2015 Premiere Dates; October Launches for All Scripted Series Including ''The Flash'' & ''Supernatural'' |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/06/24/the-cw-announces-fall-2015-premiere-dates-october-launches-for-all-scripted-series/422230/ |website=[[TV_by_the_Numbers|TV by the Numbers]] |accessdate=2015-07-05 |date=2015-06-24 |archive-date=2016-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160613002123/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/06/24/the-cw-announces-fall-2015-premiere-dates-october-launches-for-all-scripted-series/422230/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="CW Fall Updated Monday">{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/07/31/the-cw-moves-jane-the-virgin-crazy-ex-girlfriend-premieres-up-to-monday-october-12/440459/|title=The CW Moves 'Jane the Virgin' &'Crazy Ex-Girlfriend' Premieres Up to Monday October 12|last=Kondolojy|first=Amanda|work=TV by the Numbers|date=2015-07-31|accessdate=2015-07-31|archive-date=2016-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160621071907/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/07/31/the-cw-moves-jane-the-virgin-crazy-ex-girlfriend-premieres-up-to-monday-october-12/440459/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>本劇由[[瑞秋·布魯姆|瑞秋·布魯姆]]與{{link-en|愛琳·布洛許·麥肯納|Aline Brosh McKenna}}開創，並由瑞秋·布魯姆主演，同時身兼執行製作。

2016年於[[第73屆金球獎|第73屆金球獎]]中，[[瑞秋·布魯姆|瑞秋·布魯姆]]以新人之姿擊退上一屆得主[[吉娜·羅德里奎|吉娜·羅德里奎]]（《[[處女情緣|處女情緣]]》）、第46屆[[金球獎|金球獎]]得主[[潔美·李·寇蒂斯|潔美·李·寇蒂斯]]（《[[尖叫女王|尖叫女王]]》）、[[黃金時段艾美獎|第64–67屆黃金時段艾美獎]]得主[[茱莉亞·路易斯-德瑞弗斯|茱莉亞·路易斯-德瑞弗斯]]（《[[副人之仁|副人之仁]]》）以及6項[[艾美獎|艾美獎]]得主[[莉莉·湯姆琳|莉莉·湯姆琳]]（《[[同妻俱樂部|同妻俱樂部]]》），奪下電視音樂與喜劇類最佳女演員獎，並是繼吉娜·羅德里奎後，連續第2位為The CW奪下此獎的女演員。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.goldenglobes.com/winners-nominees/best-performance-actress-television-series-comedy-or-musical|title=Winners & Nominees Best Performance by an Actress In A Television Series – Comedy Or Musical|publisher=[[好萊塢外國記者協會|好萊塢外國記者協會]]|accessdate=2015-12-10|archive-date=2016-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160110094402/http://www.goldenglobes.com/winners-nominees/best-performance-actress-television-series-comedy-or-musical|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=GoldenGlobe2016>{{cite news|url=http://deadline.com/2016/01/golden-globe-winners-2016-golden-globes-awards-winner-list-1201679616/|title=2016 Golden Globes Winners: The Complete List|date=2016-01-10|work=Deadline.com|accessdate=2016-01-22|archive-date=2021-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210215041216/https://deadline.com/2016/01/golden-globe-winners-2016-golden-globes-awards-winner-list-1201679616/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年4月2日，本劇獲The CW第4季續訂，<ref name="Season 4 Renewals"/>為劇集的最終季，<ref name="CEG IZ JTV"/>預計於2018年10月首播。<ref name="CW 2018-19">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2018/05/the-cw-fall-2018-19-schedule-upfronts-new-shows-charmed-supergirl-the-flash-dynasty-1202392851/|title=The CW Fall 2018-19 Schedule: ‘Supergirl’ Moves To Sunday, Paired With ‘Charmed’; ‘Arrow’ To ‘Monday; ‘Jane’ To Midseason|author=Nellie Andreeva|author2=Denise Petski|work=Deadline.com|date=2018-05-17|accessdate=2018-05-17|archive-date=2018-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180517223236/http://deadline.com/2018/05/the-cw-fall-2018-19-schedule-upfronts-new-shows-charmed-supergirl-the-flash-dynasty-1202392851/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 故事 ==
講述一名事業有成的律師蕾貝卡·邦奇，為了追尋前男友喬許的蹤跡，而放棄了法律事務所的合夥人提議以及位於曼哈頓的高級公寓，來到喬許的家鄉－一個充滿異國浪漫情調與冒險的[[加利福尼亞州|加州]][[西柯汶納|西科維納]]。

