ditional Episodes|publisher=Deadline.com|author=Denise Petski|date=2015-11-23|accessdate=2017-04-11|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108091531/https://deadline.com/2015/11/crazy-ex-girlfriend-izombie-additional-episode-orders-1201635872/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

