=== 創作背景 ===
愛琳在觀賞布魯姆於[[YouTube|YouTube]]上的音樂作品《如果迪士尼卡通是正史》（{{lang|en|''If Disney Cartoons Were Historically Accurate''}}）後，主動與其聯繫並共同創作了本劇，然而在被Showtime取消製作後，她們嘗試向其他電視網投遞劇集，但卻在一天內被六家電視網回絕，直到她們看見《[[處女情緣|貞愛好孕到]]》的成功，遂決定接洽The CW。在經過兩天的思慮，The CW主席[[馬克·佩德維茲|馬克·佩德維茲]]給予了本劇系列預訂，劇集才得以起死回生。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-v1taKP7_S4|title=Rachel Bloom: Golden Globe Awards Backstage Interview (2016)|publisher=YouTube|author=ScreenSlam|date=2016-01-12|accessdate=2017-11-15|archive-date=2017-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170322095215/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-v1taKP7_S4|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/tv/news/watch-rachel-blooms-spirited-golden-globes-speech-20160110|title=Watch Rachel Bloom's 'Crazy' Golden Globes 2016 Speech|publisher=[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石雜誌]]|author=Brittany Spanos|date=2016-01-10|accessdate=2017-11-15|archive-date=2017-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171116034543/http://www.rollingstone.com/tv/news/watch-rachel-blooms-spirited-golden-globes-speech-20160110|dead-url=no}}</ref>在創作初期，劇組稱本劇為「50小時的電影」，因此布魯姆計畫本劇將有4季，或許能夠延續至第5季，但在創作上，她認為用4季的長度來講述故事是最理想的。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/crazy-girlfriend-rachel-bloom-talks-884798|title='Crazy Ex-Girlfriend': Rachel Bloom Talks Finale, 4-Season Plan and Musical Wish List|publisher=[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]]|author=Michael O'Connell|date=2016-04-18|accessdate=2017-09-27|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211195004/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/crazy-girlfriend-rachel-bloom-talks-884798|dead-url=no}}</ref>

