== 評價 ==
《瘋狂前女友》播出後，獲得電視評論家的一致好評。在[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]整合的評論中，第1季獲得了96%的新鮮度、7.71/10分（54位評論家）；評論家普遍共識：「活潑的音樂劇場面與清新、精力充沛的主演[[瑞秋·布魯姆|瑞秋·布魯姆]]，讓《瘋狂前女友》以迷人又古怪的方式旁觀人際關係」。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/crazy-ex-girlfriend/s01/ |title= Crazy Ex-girlfriend: Season 1 (2015) |publisher= [[爛番茄|爛番茄]] |accessdate= 2015-10-10 |archive-date= 2019-04-18 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190418083840/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/crazy-ex-girlfriend/s01 |dead-url= no }}</ref>在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]整合的評論中，第1季獲得78分（滿分100分；23位評論家），屬普遍的好評。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/crazy-ex-girlfriend |title=Crazy Ex-Girlfriend - Season 1 Reviews |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2015-10-10 |archive-date=2021-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124190448/https://www.metacritic.com/tv/crazy-ex-girlfriend |dead-url=no }}</ref>

第2季的評論更勝第1季，在爛番茄整合的評論中，獲得了100%的新鮮度、9.0/10分（13位評論家）；評論家普遍共識：「《瘋狂前女友》第2季依舊風趣古怪、引人入勝，甚至更加勇敢並充滿自信」。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/crazy-ex-girlfriend/s02/ |title= Crazy Ex-girlfriend: Season 2 (2016) |publisher= 爛番茄 |accessdate= 2016-11-24 |archive-date= 2016-11-25 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20161125045537/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/crazy-ex-girlfriend/s02/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>在Metacritic整合的評論中，獲得86分（滿分100分；8位評論家），屬極佳的讚譽。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/crazy-ex-girlfriend/season-2 |title=Crazy Ex-Girlfriend - Season 2 Reviews |publisher=Metacritic |accessdate=2016-11-24 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108141047/http://www.metacritic.com/tv/crazy-ex-girlfriend/season-2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]將本劇第二季評為“前20大最佳電視節目”中之第11名。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/gallery/best-worst-tv-shows-2016|title=The 20 Best (And 5 Worst!) TV Shows of 2016|publisher=娛樂周刊|author=Jeff Jensen|date=2016-12-08|accessdate=2016-12-11|archive-date=2016-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161211044932/http://www.ew.com/gallery/best-worst-tv-shows-2016|dead-url=no}}</ref>

第3季依舊獲得許多好評，在爛番茄整合的評論中，獲得了100%的新鮮度、8.6/10分（12位評論家）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/crazy-ex-girlfriend/s03/|title= Crazy Ex-girlfriend: Season 3|publisher=爛番茄|accessdate=2017-10-22}}</ref>

